@milanlund is right. The Form Builder is kinda limited (a bit more limited than in KX13) because it uses a different technology stack than the latest version of Xperience's Page Builder.

We know about this limitation, but any feedback you can provide via [roadmap.kentico.com](https://roadmap.kentico.com/tabs/6-next-refreshes) is welcome!

I can't commit to any dates, but you might see big improvements to how forms and the Form Builder works in Xperience toward the middle of next year, similar to how we will soon begin rolling out a much improved email authoring experience [with the Email Builder](https://roadmap.kentico.com/c/142-create-emails-using-an-email-builder).
